text:
Because of my compromised immune system, my doctor has sent me to get a #CovidVaccine booster. Shot #3. The second shot left me feeling a bit shaky and sick for a couple days. I hope this one isn't any worse. It's worth it, though.
#vaccine #Moderna #Covid19 #SickNotWeak
